msgstr ""

#: ../iot/homeassistant/install_and_configure_esphome.rst:17
msgid ""
"Here’s a very quick introduction to how ESPHome works: ESPHome is a tool "
"which aims to make managing your ESP boards as simple as possible. It "
"reads in a YAML configuration file (just like Home Assistant) and creates"
" custom firmware which it installs on your ESP device. Devices or sensors"
" added in ESPHome’s configuration will automatically show up in Home "
"Assistant’s UI."
msgstr ""

