msgid ""
"Now start to add other components. There are a lot of components in the "
"`ESPHome official website <https://esphome.io/>`_, including **Sensor "
"Components**, **Output Components**, **Light Components**, etc., Here we "
"take **Binary Light** in **Light Components** as an example."
msgstr ""

